Definition: especially of Americas) having yellow flowers and large leaves whose juice is used as a cure for ringworm and poisonous bites
Example: sometimes placed in genus Cassia
Synonyms: ringworm_shrub, ringworm_cassia, Senna_alata, Cassia_alata, senna, noun, location, US, r, tropical, shrub, especially, of, Americas, having, yellow, flowers, and, large, leaves, whose, juice, is, used, as, a, cure, for, ringworm, poisonous, bites, sometimes, placed, in, genus, Cassia
Category: noun.plant
